sub_title: Tech enthusiast | Quantum Computing | Adventure seeker
summary:
An enthusiast with a passion for tech and crazy adventures. Drove from Amsterdam to Hong Kong in 4 months, ice skated the longest race in the world and competed in the most iconic marathon event in the world. I am never disappointed when a challenge is finished, just looking forward to the next one.

My focus is on cutting edge technologies, specifically quantum computing and how to leverage this exiting upcoming technology. I am a contributor and maintainer of the Quantum Katas, a great open source learning resource for Quantum Computing.
